name: v12.133.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Trigger layer version update in documentation by @rithikanarayan in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/703
* Revert "Trigger layer version update in documentation" by @rithikanarayan in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/705
* chore: change the warning to debug log by @joeyzhao2018 in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/706
* use leaner install of dd-trace and remove hack around it by @rochdev in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/701
* update node version for update deps ci to node 20 by @ojproductions in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/708
* fix: preserve json structure when patching within this library by @duncanista in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/709
* fix missing pprof dependency by @rochdev in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/711
* v12.133.0 by @ojproductions in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/714

arn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node18-x:133
